# Component Structure

The project follows a component-based architecture using React and Tailwind CSS.

## Main Components

- `<Header />` - Top navigation bar
- `<Footer />` - Page footer
- `<SearchBar />` - Search input for filtering prompts
- `<FilterBar />` - Filtering options for platforms and categories
- `<PromptCard />` - Card display for individual prompts

